name: ReedCast
0:
”Alexa, open ReedCast”
”Alexa, ask ReedCast how my clarinet reeds will be today”
”Alexa, ask ReedCast if my oboe reeds are working”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: reed cast
des: Oboe, clarinet, bassoon, and saxophone players know their reeds can change quickly, and usually not for the better. ReedCast™ can predict the quality of your reeds with up-to-the-minute accuracy. (Or at least it can guess about as well as you can.)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
